                <a href="hh-zizhi.html" class="branch-card" style="text-decoration:none; color:inherit; display:block;">
                    <div class="branch-icon">📍</div>
                    <h4>怀化分公司</h4>
                    <p>经开区<br>柒星广场二期4楼411室</p>
